          "text": "To reduce mortality & incidence of TB by 90% under the Stop TB initiative",
          "correct": false
        },
        {
          "label": "D",
          "text": "To reduce incidence of TB by 80% under Sustainable Development Goals",
          "correct": true
        }
      ],
      "correct_answer": "D. To reduce incidence of TB by 80% under Sustainable Development Goals",
