      "explanation": "<table cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:624px\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:bottom\">\n<p><strong>Indicator</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:bottom\">\n<p><strong>Description</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:bottom\">\n<p>Completeness of reporting</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:bottom\">\n<p>At least 80% of expected routine <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"433e48b0c616927771801040d9bde9\">AFP</span> surveillance reports are to be received on time, including <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"116e588c7b1692777202c7f3040428\">zero</span> reports(no <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"433e48b0c616927771801040d9bde9\">AFP</span> cases seen).</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:bottom\">\n<p>Sensitivity of surveillance</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:bottom\">\n<p>Detect at least one case of non-polio <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"433e48b0c616927771801040d9bde9\">AFP</span> annually per 100,000 population aged <15 years (two per 100,000 in <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"59c8c1e4b316927771873c98afae15\">endemic</span> regions).(operational efficiency-non <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"7b1b23cdec1692777196fb5ec9f3f5\">polio</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"433e48b0c616927771801040d9bde9\">AFP</span> rate)</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:bottom\">\n<p>Completeness of case investigation</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:bottom\">\n<p>All <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"433e48b0c616927771801040d9bde9\">AFP</span> cases undergo full clinical and virological investigation with at least 80% of cases having adequate <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"44335bb8bf1692777199a956cb31bf\">stool</span> specimens collected and transported properly.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:bottom\">\n<p>Completeness of follow-up</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:bottom\">\n<p>At least 80% of <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"433e48b0c616927771801040d9bde9\">AFP</span> cases receive a follow-up examination for <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"a459f313d9169277719789fdfb7ada\">residual</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"72fa9105b916927771945aef35e8ed\">paralysis</span> at 60 days post-onset.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:bottom\">\n<p>Laboratory performance</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:bottom\">\n<p>AFP case specimens are processed in WHO-accredited laboratories within the Global <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"7b1b23cdec1692777196fb5ec9f3f5\">Polio</span> Laboratory Network (GPLN).</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n\n\n<p style='font-size: 10px; color: #808080; font-style: italic;'></p>",
